Senior Editor
- ,
Date Posted: 2014/05/02 08:23:33
Ref. JB3046579
Job Description
* Main Accountabilities :
• Responsible for the content and images used on a website.
• Filter Middle East news and post articles with updated market information.
• Plan, research, write copy and edit the content of a website.
• Liaise with clients and internal departments.
• Maintain the site and ensure the information is accurate and attractive.
* Job Description :
Subjects :
• Web Master, producing new content and writing it in an interesting and appealing manner.
• Source images and artwork.
• Upload banners for the upcoming shows.
• Continuously monitor that the website is running properly.
• Prepare weekly newsletters including articles about market information and latest industry news and upcoming IFP exhibitions and shows.
• Coordinate with PR agencies outside Lebanon to get the needed information and pictures from the exhibitors abroad.
• Conduct interviews with the exhibitors and the sponsors during IFP events and publish the interviews in the newsletters and on the website.
• Conduct research about new markets as requested by the management.
• Provide Project Managers with market and industry information.
• Manage IFP Social Media pages.
• Perform special tasks assigned by the management.
Skills
• Good command of Arabic and English.
• Excellent Verbal and Written communication skills.
• Inquisitive mind.
• Creative.
Education
BA degree in Journalism, Political Science, or English Literature
