About This Company
We are a leading international exhibitions and conferences organizer based in Beirut with operational offices throughout the Middle East. We have been in business for over 30 years and cover many industry sectors.
We offer a comprehensive range of trade fair services executed to the highest international standards. These include full logistical support, on-site stand builders, furniture hire, signs and graphics.
Our events are attended by local, regional and international big name companies and we are supported by various international organizations and independent agents.
